  "_comment": "Hard-coded EMBEDDED banner map for name-keyed services (Blizzard/Battle.net + Riot) that have no Steam appId / Epic catalog id. Each value is an 'embedded://{slug}' sentinel that resolves to the embedded resource LancacheManager.banners.{slug}.jpg (the 32 JPEGs under Infrastructure/Data/banners/). These banners are composited/curated OFFLINE and the embedded bytes are the SOLE source - GameImageFetchService loads them via NameKeyedBannerSource.TryGetEmbeddedBytes and NEVER fetches or auto-updates them over the network (no startup fetch, no 7-day refresh, no HTTP on clear-cache re-seed). Keys MUST match the exact GameName strings produced by BattleNetMappingService (rust-processor/tact_products.json) and the Riot service. Loaded at runtime by GameImageFetchService via Assembly.GetManifestResourceStream(\"LancacheManager.game_banners.json\").",
